suppose you are sitting on a node and you want to submit a certain test 
from a list of nodes

so there are three tests:

1) write 
2) read
3) torture read 

you need to modify *_setup.sh files for each of the test, so 3 files:

        write_setup.sh
        read_setup.sh
        torture_setup.sh

you need to build too binary files:

        g++ gauss.cc -o gauss
        g++ createfile.cc -o createfile



*setup.sh files will copy all what they need to execution nodes. 
write tests will create files with unique names.


